This paper discusses the development of ontologies to support the sharing and exchange of research data and methods, which falls under the category of digital libraries (cs.DL) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The paper also mentions the use of specialized repositories for sharing datasets, which could fall under databases (cs.DB). Additionally, the paper discusses the need for models to capture the life cycle of scientific investigations, which could fall under cybernetics (cs.CY) or software engineering (cs.SE).
